name: Expat Serbia BELEX15 UCITS ETF
description_en: The Expat Serbia BELEX15 UCITS ETF seeks to track the BELEX15 index. The BELEX15 index tracks the main Serbian companies. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 1.38% p.a.. The Expat Serbia BELEX15 UCITS ETF is the only ETF that tracks the BELEX15 index. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by full replication (buying all the index constituents). The dividends in the ETF are accumulated and reinvested in the ETF. The Expat Serbia BELEX15 UCITS ETF is a very small ETF with 0m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 5 February 2018 and is domiciled in Bulgaria. Show more Show less

name: iShares Core CHF Corporate Bond ETF (CH) CHF (Dist)
description_en: The iShares Core CHF Corporate Bond ETF (CH) CHF (Dist) seeks to track the SBI® Corporate index. The SBI® Corporate index tracks Swiss Franc denominated corporate bonds. The ETF's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.15% p.a.. The ETF replicates the performance of the underlying index by sampling technique (buying a selection of the most relevant index constituents). The interest income (coupons) in the ETF is distributed to the investors (Semi annually). The iShares Core CHF Corporate Bond ETF (CH) CHF (Dist) is a very large ETF with 1,991m Euro assets under management. The ETF was launched on 14 January 2014 and is domiciled in Switzerland. Show more Show less

name: 21Shares Crypto Basket Index ETP
description_en: The 21Shares Crypto Basket index tracks the performance of the top five cryptocurrencies (as measured by market capitalisation). The ETN's TER (total expense ratio) amounts to 0.99% p.a.. The 21Shares Crypto Basket Index ETP is the only ETN that tracks the 21Shares Crypto Basket index. The ETN replicates the performance of the underlying index with a collateralised debt obligation which is backed by physical holdings of the cryptocurrency. The 21Shares Crypto Basket Index ETP has 225m Euro assets under management. The ETN was launched on 21 November 2018 and is domiciled in Switzerland. Show more Show less
description_cs: Index krypto koše 21 Shares sleduje výkon pěti nejlepších kryptoměn (měřeno tržní kapitalizací).ETN TER (celkový poměr nákladů) činí 0,99% P.A .. Index 21shares Crypto Basket ETP je jediný ETN, který sleduje index krypto koše 21Shares.ETN replikuje výkon podkladového indexu s zajištěným dluhovým závazkem, který je podporován fyzickými drženími kryptoměny.ETP indexu krypto koše 21 Shares má pod správou aktiva 225 milionů EUR.ETN byl spuštěn 21. listopadu 2018 a má bydliště ve Švýcarsku.Ukázat více show méně
